== Building Selenium IDE ==

You will need Apache Ant, so download it from http://ant.apache.org/

Copy build.properties.sample to build.properties,
and set selenium.src to the Selenium source directory.

Run ant and you will get build/seleniumrecorder.xpi.

== Running unit tests ==

You can run internal tests of Selenium IDE using JsUnit by visiting following URL:

chrome://selenium-ide/content/tests/index.html

